{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 2 shows three examples, while a full set of the sentences can be found in the GitHub repository (see link in Code Availability section).",
    "Furthermore, the LLM showed an F1 score of 89.47% on the relationship extraction task.",
    "Additionally, we looked at the same metrics for a zero-shot version of the same LLM, and while the F1 score remained high at 88.23%, the recognition scores for phases and properties were much lower at 28.47% and 46.00%, respectively.",
    "Some sentences in our dataset mentioned multiple phases and/or properties.",
    "For example, for a sentence containing \"phase A, phase B, and phase C increase property X,\" we aim to extract three individual relationships between the three phases and the property."
  ]
}